title: Cute One Bedroom in Powderhorn
posting_body: ['Available for September 1st move-in.', 'A cozy and warm one bedroom unit on the 2nd floor.', 'High ceiling and spacious bedroom.', 'Located on the corner of 31st and 12th Ave.', 'One block from Powderhorn park.', 'Description:', '-Hardwood floors in bedroom and living room', '-Great kitchen', '-Two closets in unit and storage closet in basement.', '-Free basement laundry', '-Gas stove', '-Great water pressure', '-High ceilings', '-The feel of the house is more of community than "oh that other person upstairs"', '-Wonderful fenced in yard with garden beds, outdoor patio for meals, fire pit, and chickens!', '-One off-street parking spot for this unit in back', 'Location:', '-One short block from Powderhorn park', '-Food all around on Lake Street (Taco truck at end of alley:)', '-Bus stop on north end of our block', '-Great neighbors', '-So much sun in living space', 'Lease Terms', '-$1,100 Monthly rent (Includes all utilities)', '-All utilities (Internet, Gas, Water, Electric, sewer, trash)', '-12 month lease then month to month', '-Security deposit is 1 month of rent', 'Application process', "-Background check required ($40) will reimburse if doesn't work out", '-Application form which includes employment history', 'Come take a tour!']
